story: Pwnky, a creature from the Farm of Inpinity Online, ventured through the digital realms with Light blue eyes  eyes that sparkled with curiosity, a Mechanic body body that shimmered with the essence of creativity, and a Shocked open mouth  mouth that resonated with the voices of countless creators. On this journey, Pwnky's Comic ear ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Long blue hair hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Astronaut suite  hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Glasses, a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
description: a new Pwnkey with Farm, Light blue eyes , Mechanic body, Shocked open mouth , Comic ear, Long blue hair, Astronaut suite , Glasses
